have a drinking problem.

17:04.625 --> 17:07.208
-No. Mom has a <i>Heather </i>problem.
-Yeah.

17:07.291 --> 17:09.834
Matt, you are moving up
in the world.

17:09.917 --> 17:11.875
-Welcome to the top two kids.
-Yeah.

17:11.959 --> 17:14.083
I hope you enjoy
inside jokes about Matt.

17:14.166 --> 17:15.500
I mean, Heather.

17:15.583 --> 17:17.375
Jokes about Heather.

