17:26.291 --> 17:28.208
and-and we've noticed
that, uh,

17:28.291 --> 17:30.500
well, you seem
a little bit overwhelmed

17:30.583 --> 17:32.166
by having Heather here.

17:32.250 --> 17:35.959
Oh, no, no. It-It's joyous.

17:36.041 --> 17:39.083
It's like when a comet blazes
into the atmosphere,

17:39.166 --> 17:42.709
and primitive people everywhere
think the world is ending,

17:42.792 --> 17:45.500
and yet it may never come again
in your lifetime,

17:45.583 --> 17:47.625
and so you should treasure it.

17:47.709 --> 17:50.083
You do know that it is okay

17:50.166 --> 17:52.625
