18:05.083 --> 18:06.500
Where's <i>JAG, </i>damn it?

18:06.583 --> 18:07.959
They don't make it anymore,

18:08.041 --> 18:10.000
and once you delete it,
they're gone forever.

18:10.083 --> 18:13.208
Yeah, okay.
Mom, the first step

18:13.291 --> 18:14.875
